---
// Hero.astro - 2026 MCPC 官方風格 (Tailwind 版)
---

<section id="home" class="relative pt-[150px] pb-[90px] lg:pt-[180px] lg:pb-[100px] overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-bg-light to-white">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.06]" 
             style="background-image: linear-gradient(#2E86AB 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #2E86AB 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 52px 52px; mix-blend-mode: multiply;">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-[8%] left-[6%] w-[360px] h-[360px] bg-[#2E86AB]/25 rounded-full blur-[60px] animate-float opacity-35"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[8%] w-[420px] h-[420px] bg-blue-400/25 rounded-full blur-[60px] animate-float opacity-35" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[45%] w-[520px] h-[520px] bg-bg-light/90 rounded-full blur-[60px] animate-float opacity-55" style="animation-delay: 2.4s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] gap-12 lg:gap-[70px] items-center">
            
            <div class="text-left">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-bg-light/95 text-primary-dark border border-primary/15 rounded-full font-bold text-sm mb-6 animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
                    <span class="text-primary">✨</span> 2026 年度競賽
                </div>

                <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem] font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4 leading-tight tracking-wide animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
                    行動通訊
                    <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-dark bg-clip-text text-transparent mt-2">實務競賽</span>
                </h1>

                <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
                    連結智慧，驅動未來。邀請全國大專院校學生參與，展現專業實力，角逐豐厚獎金與榮譽。
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-10 animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
                    <a href="/registration" class="px-8 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                        立即報名 →
                    </a>
                    <a href="/downloads" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-primary border-2 border-primary rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                        下載簡章
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-3 pr-5 shadow-sm min-w-[180px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30 cursor-default">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 grid place-items-center rounded-xl bg-bg-light/95 text-xl">📅</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">報名截止</div>
                            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">2026.03.01</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-3 pr-5 shadow-sm min-w-[180px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30 cursor-default">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 grid place-items-center rounded-xl bg-bg-light/95 text-xl">🧾</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">初賽結果</div>
                            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">2026.04.01</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-3 pr-5 shadow-sm min-w-[180px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary/30 cursor-default">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 grid place-items-center rounded-xl bg-bg-light/95 text-xl">🏁</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">決賽日期</div>
                            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">2026.04.20</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden lg:flex justify-center relative animate-fade-up opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
                <div class="relative w-[420px] aspect-square">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/25 animate-spin-slow"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-7 border-2 border-dashed border-primary/30 rounded-full animate-spin-slow" style="animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 16s;"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-[70px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark shadow-2xl shadow-primary/35 grid place-items-center text-white text-center z-10">
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-[5rem] font-black leading-none">M</div>
                            <div class="text-sm font-bold opacity-90 tracking-widest mt-1">CPC 2026</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute top-[6%] -right-[2%] bg-white/95 backdrop-blur border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-3 shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3 animate-float rotate-6 z-20 min-w-[160px]">
                        <div class="w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-xl bg-bg-light text-xl">🏆</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">總獎金</div>
                            <div class="text-lg font-black text-slate-800">NT$ 50萬</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-[12%] -left-[2%] bg-white/95 backdrop-blur border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-3 shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3 animate-float -rotate-6 z-20 min-w-[160px]" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
                        <div class="w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-xl bg-bg-light text-xl">👥</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">參賽隊伍</div>
                            <div class="text-lg font-black text-slate-800">100+ 組</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>